[FILE PHOTO]  Dead body At least three persons  have died and 284 persons hospitalised as strange disease hit Kano city, Kano State Government said on Tuesday. The disease has spread across the eight metropolitan councils and five more local government areas in the state. Commissioner for Health Dr. Aminu Ibrahim Tsanyawa said preliminary investigation revealed that affected persons developed various “strange” symptoms after drinking water from a borehole sunk near cemetery.  To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .